      <div class="booking-step-content" id="bs-5">
        <div class="success-msg">
          <div class="checkmark">✅</div>
          <h3>Appointment Booked!</h3>
          <p>Thank you! Your appointment at <strong>Laishaz Studio</strong> has been confirmed. We'll send a reminder before your visit.</p>
